metadata.name: Itsuki Derivative #5948
metadata.description:
Created by Katalina-Ooma [Artstation](https://www.artstation.com/katalina_ooma)

A derivative art piece representing [Itsuki lady #5948](https://opensea.io/assets/ethereum/0x25692da406889bf4db93f921063d9bc952bd01d0/5948/) from the special [We are Itsuki](https://opensea.io/collection/itsuki-v2) verified collection. Designed and produced in Clip Studio Paint Pro and Adobe Photoshop, with the special help of Midjourney textures. 

#ItsukiClanClash
